flowchart TD
  subgraph Register
    R1[POST /auth/register] --> R2[Validate RegisterDto]
    R2 --> R3[Check email uniqueness]
    R3 --> R4[Hash password with bcrypt]
    R4 --> R5[Prisma transaction]
    R5 --> R6[Create user]
    R6 --> R7[Create default categories]
    R7 --> R8[Generate access and refresh JWTs]
    R8 --> R9[Store refresh token SHA-256 digest]
    R9 --> R10[Return public user and tokens]
  end

  subgraph Login
    L1[POST /auth/login] --> L2[Validate LoginDto]
    L2 --> L3[Load user with password]
    L3 --> L4[Compare bcrypt password]
    L4 --> L5[Generate token pair]
    L5 --> L6[Rotate stored refresh digest]
    L6 --> L7[Return public user and tokens]
  end

  subgraph VerifyAccess
    V1[Protected request] --> V2[JwtAuthGuard]
    V2 --> V3[JwtStrategy verifies access token]
    V3 --> V4[Attach userId email role]
    V4 --> V5[Controller receives request.user]
  end

  subgraph RBAC
    A1[@Roles metadata] --> A2[RolesGuard]
    A2 --> A3{Role allowed?}
    A3 -->|yes| A4[Route handler]
    A3 -->|no| A5[FORBIDDEN_ACCESS]
  end

  subgraph Refresh
    F1[POST /auth/refresh] --> F2[Verify refresh JWT]
    F2 --> F3[Compare stored digest]
    F3 --> F4[Load public user]
    F4 --> F5[Generate new token pair]
    F5 --> F6[Rotate refresh digest]
    F6 --> F7[Return new tokens]
  end

  subgraph Logout
    O1[POST /auth/logout] --> O2[JwtAuthGuard]
    O2 --> O3[Set refreshToken null]
    O3 --> O4[Return loggedOut true]
  end
